    "**Data Aggregation**\n",
    "\n",
    "Using NumPy Functions for Summary Statistics:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "6389874a-bb8e-4c6d-9f7c-3c487ecba683",
